CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 10 reads: "AKA'S Initiate - These charming young ladies were initiated into Iota Chapter of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority June 25. Pictured are Joan Bolden, Barbara Peace, Hildegarde Boswell, Seephanie Johnson, Patricia Myatt, Monretta Davis, Edythe Schrader, Shirley Powe and Joanne Snyder. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority initiates: Joan Bolden, Barbara Peace, Hildegarde Boswell, Seephanie Johnson, Patricia Myatt, Monretta Davis, Edythe Schrader, Shirley Powe and Joanne Snyder, posed in interior with fine patterned wallpaper, linoleum floor inscribed "R...E...", and stairs
